# Normalise line endings for the whole repo. Everything is stored as LF in the
# repository, and checked out as LF in the working tree — matching what our
# tooling (bun, tauri, vite codegen) writes. `eol=lf` overrides each developer's
# `core.autocrlf`, so nobody's machine config can reintroduce CRLF churn.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Treat binary assets as binary so Git never applies line-ending conversion.
*.mp3 binary
*.wav binary
*.ogg binary
*.flac binary
*.pdf binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.gif binary
